comment: /**  * Returns the underlying `AmazonEC2` client. All method calls are permitted BUT  * NOT shutdown. Shutdown is called when reference count reaches 0.  */
code: /**  * Returns the underlying `AmazonEC2` client. All method calls are permitted BUT  * NOT shutdown. Shutdown is called when reference count reaches 0.  */ public AmazonEC2 client() {     return client. }
